    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="topic" onclick="toggleQuestions('topic1')"><h3>Seller FAQ's </h3></div>
    <div class="questions" id="topic1">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer1')">Q1.How do I create a seller account?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer1">To create a seller account, visit our website and click on the "Sell" or "Become a Seller" option. Follow the prompts to provide the required information and set up your account.</div>

        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer2')">Q2. What are the fees for selling on this platform?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer2">Our fees vary depending on the type of product and the plan you choose. You can find detailed fee information in your seller dashboard.</div>
        
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer3')">Q3. How do I list my products for sale?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer3">After creating an account, go to your seller dashboard and click on "List a Product." Follow the steps to provide product details, pricing, and images.</div>

        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer4')">Q4. What payment methods are available for sellers?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer4">We offer various payment methods, including direct deposit, check, or PayPal. You can choose the one that suits you best.</div>
    
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer5')">Q5. How can I manage my orders and shipping?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer3"> You can manage orders through your seller dashboard. We also provide shipping and fulfillment options, including integration with shipping carriers.</div>

    </div>

    <div class="topic" onclick="toggleQuestions('topic2')"><h3>Buyer FAQ's</h3></div>
    <div class="questions" id="topic2">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer6')">Q1. How do I create a buyer account?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer6">Creating a buyer account is simple. Click on "Sign Up" or "Create Account" and provide your details to register.</div>

        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer7')">Q2. Is my payment information secure when making a purchase?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer7">Yes, we take security seriously. We use encryption and secure payment gateways to protect your financial information.</div>
        
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer8')">Q3. hat is your return policy?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer8">Our return policy varies by seller and product. Check the product listing and seller's return policy for specific details.</div>

        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer9')">Q4. How can I track my order?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer9">You can track your order through your buyer account or by using the tracking number provided by the seller.</div>
    
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer10')">Q5. What if I have an issue with a purchase?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer10">If you have any issues, contact the seller first. If the problem persists, our customer support team is here to assist you.</div>

    </div>

        <div class="topic" onclick="toggleQuestions('topic3')"><h3>General Queries</h3></div>
    <div class="questions" id="topic3">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer31')">Q1. How can I reset my password?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer31">To reset your password, click on "Forgot Password" on the login page and follow the instructions sent to your email.</div>

        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer32')">Q2. Can I change my shipping address after placing an order?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer32">Contact the seller as soon as possible to request a change in the shipping address.</div>
    
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer33')">Q3. What should I do if I forget my username or email?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer33">Contact our customer support for assistance in recovering your username or email.</div>

    </div>

    <div class="topic" onclick="toggleQuestions('topic4')"><h3>Legal Information</h3></div>
    <div class="questions" id="topic4">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer41')">Q1. What are the terms and conditions for using this platform?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer41">You can find our terms and conditions in the "Terms of Service" section on our website.</div>

        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer42')">Q2. What is your privacy policy regarding user data?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer42">Our privacy policy is available in the "Privacy Policy" section on our website. It outlines how we collect, use, and protect user data.</div>

        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer43')">Q3. How do I report copyright or trademark infringement?</div>
        <div class="answer" id="answer43">If you believe your intellectual property rights are being violated, please contact our legal team through the "Report Infringement" link provided on the website.</div>

    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleQuestions(topicId) {
            const questions = document.getElementById(topicId);
            if (questions.style.display === 'none' || questions.style.display === '') {
                questions.style.display = 'block';
            } else {
                questions.style.display = 'none';
            }
        }

        function toggleAnswer(answerId) {
            const answer = document.getElementById(answerId);
            if (answer.style.display === 'none' || answer.style.display === '') {
                answer.style.display = 'block';
            } else {
                answer.style.display = 'none';
            }
        }
    </script> 



